Installation
============

Do the following commands::

  $ ./configure
  $ make
  $ sudo make install

Then you will get ``/usr/local/bin/yog``.

If you want to install another directory, you can use the ``--prefix`` option to the configure.
If you do::

  $ ./configure --prefix=PREFIX

you will get ``PREFIX/bin/yog``.

